{
  "stem": "17330.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people knew him, because he was a representative for the firm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when we fled, I went to a customer, but they were Jewish people too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had two boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she said, OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll take you for a few days, but you can't stay here, because we don't know what happen to us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we stayed there for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the meantime, my father made contact with somebody who lived in that area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were supposed to give us a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was three months pregnant for my son, my middle son.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was working for the underground movement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Can't remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then she said to us, I've got an address.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But first, in lunchtime, you go to that and that street, that and that people, and stay there 'til the night.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the nighttime, we will pick you up and bring you to a permanent address.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So like I had an instinct that something was not OK.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said to my husband, you walk one side of the street and I walk the other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we came to a corner and there were maybe six people from the village, what you could see real village people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were standing there talking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I walked on the right side and he walked on the left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they stopped him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were walking without a star, without the David Star, and no papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not allowed to travel in a train or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they stopped him and asked him for his papers, which he didn't have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took him away.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
